cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with deep image generation and proposes a new paradigm for image reconstruction using vector layers. This involves techniques related to computer vision (cs.CV) such as image generation and image search, as well as graphics (cs.GR) such as vector graphics systems. The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed approach, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper demonstrates several applications of the new image representation, including editing and vectorization, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM).
